oei]] version)\n*''[[Zombie-Loan]]''\n\n===News programs===\n*{{nihongo|''[[all-Nippon News Network|ANN News]]''|ANN\u30cb\u30e5\u30fc\u30b9|ANN Ny\u016bsu}} (daily [[news bulletin]], [[simulcast]] at all ANN stations, weekdays at 1:59 PM and weekends at 5:50 and 11:45 AM; 2:25 (SAT), 3:25 (SUN), 5:30 and 8:54 PM)\n*''ANN News and Sports'' (Saturdays at 12:00 MN)\n*{{nihongo|''[[Good! Morning]]''|\u30b0\u30c3\u30c9!\u30e2\u30fc\u30cb\u30f3\u30b0}} (early morning show, weekdays from 4:55 to 8:00 AM)\n*{{nihongo|''[[Hai! Terebi Asahi Desu.]]''|\u306f\u3044!\u30c6\u30ec\u30d3\u671d\u65e5\u3067\u3059|Yes! This is TV Asahi.}} (public service program, 1st and 3rd Sunday of the month at 4:50 - 5:20 AM)\n*{{nihongo|''[[Hodo Station]]''|\u5831\u9053\u30b9\u30c6\u30fc\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3|Hodo Sut\u0113shon}} (late night newscast, weekdays from 9:54 to 11:10 PM)\n*{{nihongo|''[[Onegai! Morning]]''|\u304a\u9858\u3044!\u30e2\u30fc\u30cb\u30f3\u30b0}} (early morning variety show spinoff from ''Onegai! Ranking'', weekdays from 4:00 to 4:55 AM)\n*''[[Saturday Station]]'' (\u30b5\u30bf\u30c7\u30fc\u30b9\u30c6\u30fc\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3) (Saturdays from 8:54 to 10:10 PM)\n*''[[Sunday Station]]'' (\u30b5\u30f3\u30c7\u30fc\u30b9\u30c6\u30fc\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3) (Sundays from 4:30 to 6:00 PM)\n*{{nihongo|''[[Super J Channel]]''|\u30b9\u30fc\u30d1\u30fcJ\u30c1\u30e3\u30f3\u30cd\u30eb}} (evening newscast, weekdays from 4:53 to 7:00 PM and weekends from 5:30 to 5:55 PM)\n*''[[Super Morning]]'' (\u30b9\u30fc\u30d1\u30fc\u30e2\u30fc\u30cb\u30f3\u30b0) (late morning show) \n*''[[Wide! Scramble]]'' (\u30ef\u30a4\u30c9!\u30b9\u30af\u30e9\u30f3\u30d6\u30eb)\n*''[[Yaguchi Hitori Maru C]] (\u3084\u3050\u3061\u3072\u3068\u308aC)\n*''[[Sunday LIVE!!]]'' (\u30b5\u30f3\u30c7\u30fcLIVE!!)\n\n===Sports programs===\n*''[[United States Golf Association]]'':\n** ''[[U.S. Open (golf)|U.S. Open]] and [[United States Women's Open Championship (golf)| Women's Open]]\n*''[[The Royal and Ancient Golf Club of St Andrews