e Seals at Dumbarton Oaks and in the Fogg Museum of Art|volume=1|year=1991|location=Washington, D.C.|publisher=Dumbarton Oaks Research Library and Collection|url=https://www.doaks.org/research/publications/books/catalogue-of-byzantine-seals-at-dumbarton-oaks-and-in-the-fogg-museum-of-art-1-italy-north-of-the-balkans-north-of-the-black-seas|access-date=2019-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512121334/https://www.doaks.org/research/publications/books/catalogue-of-byzantine-seals-at-dumbarton-oaks-and-in-the-fogg-museum-of-art-1-italy-north-of-the-balkans-north-of-the-black-seas|archive-date=2019-05-12|url-status=dead}}\n*{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=Xoww453NVQMC&pg=PA75&dq=greek+macedonians+regional+identity#v=onepage&q=anthem&f=false |title=Collective Memory, National Identity, and Ethnic Conflict: Greece, Bulgaria, and the Macedonian Question |last=Roudometof |first=Victor |date=2002 |publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group |language=en |isbn=0275976483}}\n*{{cite book |last=Samsaris|first=Dimitrios C.|title=Historical Geography of Eastern Macedonia during the Antiquity (in Greek)|publisher=Society for Macedonian Studies,Thessaloniki  |year=1976|isbn=960-7265-16-5|url=http://media.ems.gr/ekdoseis/makedoniki_bibliothiki/ekd_makb_samsaris_049.pdf}}\n*{{cite book |last=Samsaris|first=Dimitrios C.|title=Historical Geography of the Roman province of Macedonia (The Department of Western Macedonia today) (in Greek) |publisher=Society for Macedonian Studies,Thessaloniki  |year=1989|isbn=960-7265-01-7|url=http://media.ems.gr/ekdoseis/makedoniki_bibliothiki/ekd_makb_samsaris_070.pdf}}\n*{{cite book |last=Souvatzi|first=Stella G.|title=A Social Archaeology of Households in Neolithic Greece : an Anthropological Approach |publisher=Cambridge University Press  |year=2008|isbn=978-0-521-83689-0}}\n*{{cite book |last=Treadgold |first=Warren |title=Byzantium and Its Army, 284&ndash;1081 |publisher=Stanford University Press |year=1995 |isbn=0-8047-3163-2